# 7. Domain Responsibilities

## Platform Domains

These modules belong to Halisako itself.

- Authentication
- Users
- Projects
- Uploads
- Jobs
- Orchestration
- HXT
- Storage
- Logging

These should never contain Chess-specific logic.

---

## Product Domains

Products own:

- parsing
- analysis
- planning
- mapping

Products never perform:

- authentication
- uploads
- user management
- orchestration

