# 21. Sprint 1 Definition of Done

Sprint 1 is complete when the following workflow executes successfully.

```
User Login

↓

Create Project

↓

Upload PGN

↓

Job Created

↓

Chess Analysis

↓

Generate HXT

↓

View HXT Timeline
```

No rendering engine is required for Sprint 1.

The primary deliverable is a functioning orchestration pipeline that transforms a chess game into an HXT representation.

---

# 22. Engineering Notes

The backend shall never be tightly coupled to any specific AI model, renderer, or product.

Every new experience type must integrate by implementing the standard orchestration lifecycle:

Input → Parser → Analyzer → Intent → Planner → HXT

This principle ensures that Halisako remains an extensible orchestration platform rather than a collection of unrelated AI applications.
